NPCDialogue.LocalizedString: HELLO SPROUTS! @THAT MASSIVE SCREW THING... IT'S NOT FROM OUR WORLD. @IT SEEMS THAT HUMGRUMP IS BRINGING METAL PARTS INTO OUR LAND FROM THE OUTSIDE REALM...
HE'S PILFERED ALL THAT METAL JUNK FROM ANOTHER BOOK ON THE DESK.
CAN'T BE GOOD NEWS. IT NEVER IS WITH THAT NITWIT. @HURRY UP TO THE PEAK, SEE WHAT HUMDINGUS IS UP TO! @MOONBEARD OUT!
